## Core Workflow

```
Bid/RFP Input
    ↓
SwiftCPQ (pricing/quoting)
    ↓
Proposal generated
    ↓
AWS Textract + Comprehend (parse incoming docs)
    ↓
LexNLP (clause/entity extraction)
    ↓
ContextGem (risk + intelligence layer)
    ↓
Claude API (structure, draft, refine contract)
    ↓
Accord Project template applied
    ↓
DocuSeal (eSignature + execution)
    ↓
Signed contract stored in S3
```

