## Key Business Rules

- **Pre-process before Claude** — always extract, chunk, and structure documents before any Claude API call; never pass raw file bytes
- **Accord templates are the source of truth** — contract output must conform to Accord Project schema; Claude fills fields, does not define structure
- **No PII in logs** — contract content, party names, and financial terms must be scrubbed before any logging
- **Proposal → Contract traceability** — every contract must reference its originating proposal ID in the DB
- **DocuSeal self-hosted preferred** — use cloud DocuSeal only if self-hosted infra is not available in the target environment

